<li>Cardano is actively evaluating and reducing its carbon footprint, demonstrating its commitment to sustainability.</li>



<li>The platform promotes the use of renewable energy sources and explores incorporating them into network operations.</li>



<li>Cardano&#8217;s proof-of-stake model significantly reduces energy consumption compared to traditional proof-of-work cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin and Ethereum.</li>



