<p>The evaluation of networks is crucial in comparing the carbon emissions and carbon footprint of Cardano (ADA) within the broader context of the cryptocurrency industry. </p>



<p>To accurately assess the environmental impact of Cardano, it is essential to cross-compare its carbon emissions with other cryptocurrencies. This cross-comparison allows for a better understanding of Cardano&#8217;s carbon footprint relative to its peers.</p>



