<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Energy Consumption Comparison with Traditional Cryptocurrencies</h3>



<p>By comparing its energy consumption with that of traditional cryptocurrencies, Cardano demonstrates its commitment to renewable energy sources and sustainability. </p>



<p>As a decentralized blockchain platform, Cardano utilizes a proof-of-stake (PoS) consensus mechanism, which significantly reduces its energy consumption compared to traditional cryptocurrencies that rely on proof-of-work (PoW) algorithms. This commitment to energy efficiency aligns with Cardano&#8217;s broader goal of promoting sustainability and minimizing its environmental impact.</p>



